text: Tea Pedić (born 6 September 1996) is a Croatian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Croatia women's national team. ==Career== Pedić has been capped for the Croatia national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian women's footballers Category:Croatia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:ŽNK Split players
